cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Request for Tenders for the supply of Ambient Food Products to the Houses of the Oireachtas Catering Facilities
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: The Houses of the Oireachtas Commission (the “Contracting Authority”) invites tenders (“Tenders”) to this request for tenders (“RFT”) from economic operators (“Tenderers”) for supply of the goods as described in Appendix 1 to this RFT (the “Goods”). In summary, the Goods comprise: The supply and delivery of ambient food products to the Houses of the Oireachtas Catering Facilities.
